This page documents '''items and equipment''' in '''[[Soul Blazer]]''' (SNES).

==Overview==
Soul Blazer features various equipment types that enhance the player's abilities.
Equipment is obtained by releasing souls from Soul Lairs or found in chests.

'''Item Counts:'''
* Swords: 8
* Armor: 8
* Magic: 8
* Key Items: 12
* Consumables: 3
* Emblems: 8
* '''Total: 47 unique items'''

