===Sword Attack Calculation===
<pre>
Base Damage = Sword_Attack + Player_STR
Modified Damage = Base_Damage × Multiplier

Multipliers:
- Normal hit: 1.0×
- Critical hit: 2.0×
- Elemental weakness: 1.5×
- Wrong element: 0.5×
</pre>

